<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Welcome to Project!</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
            background: #f6f8fa;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            background: #fff;
            max-width: 480px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.07);
            padding: 32px 28px;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #2b7cff;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        p {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 1.1em;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 32px;
            font-size: 0.95em;
            color: #888;
            text-align: center;
        }

        ul {
            padding-left: 0;
            margin: 0;
        }

        li {
            background: #eaf3ff;
            border-left: 4px solid #2b7cff;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            color: #234;
            font-size: 1.07em;
            font-weight: 500;
            list-style: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Welcome, <span style="white-space: nowrap;">@Model.FirstName! 🎉</span></h1>
        <p>Thank you for registering at <b>Project</b>. We're excited to have you join our community!</p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>